<h2><a name="TOC-The-purpose-of-the-Quality-theme"></a>The purpose of the Quality theme</h2>
<div></div>
<div class="sites-codeblock sites-codesnippet-block">
<div><code>The purpose of the Quality theme is to <b>define</b> <u>and</u> <b>implement</b> the means by which the project will verify that products are fit for purpose.</code></div>
<div></div>
</div>
<br>
<div>Quality is an intrinsic part of the project, one of the six aspects of project management and needs to be part of planning to ensure that:</div>
<div>
<ul><li>Time is allocated for quality procedures</li>
<li>Time and resources are allocated to make the product fit for purpose (manufacturing costs etc)</li>
<li>It forms part of the definition of the scope of the project.</li></ul>
<div><br>
</div>
</div>
